Look these factions up on Allakazam and find out how you raise your standing with them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unesallas.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nesallas</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(8/11/01 10:04:48 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PoG faction (help meeee)</span><hr size=1> If you kill in  Pog  like I did  you can still do  your epic.  I had to hand  Pandos Flintside in  Hogcallers Inn  in  WFP 8000+ muffins  in order to go from  Scowl to Ally. you can buy muffins  at the inns in  EK&lt;use Evac&gt;. and then  run to FP.  Hand him 16 at a time  4 in each slot  and eventually you can raise your faction high enough  to do your epic.  <br>
<br>
The only faction hit you take in Pog that you can't raise and that is Inhabitants of Growth, but seeing as how I follow  Karana I have no reason to be in  POG  ever.<br>
<br>
